{"tid":188812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本票選「看到她演戲就轉台」女演員 Top 10 模特兒轉戰女優全都中招...","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T09:21:11.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66fa125b081c1efa03b034b5b8c6012972d6bc05","tid":188812,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"日劇長年以來一直都相當盛行，而在日本演藝圈中，能夠被冠上女演員這一個封號也幾乎都是眾女星所追求的地位，不論是雜誌模特兒、偶像幾乎人人的志向都是成為女演員，雖然現在要被媒體稱為「女優」已經不是太困難的事情，但要被觀眾認同可就不是件容易的事情了。日本網站 goo 最新舉辦了看劇時真心覺得她不適合演戲的女星 Top 10，或許也能夠讓觀眾產生共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n第 10 名、武井咲。<br />\n從國民美少女選拔一路獲經紀公司力推的新生代女演員，23 歲的武井咲雖然資源極好，但幾乎都被觀眾歸類為演戲不佳的那一群。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e30018d4211.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e30018d4211.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=cf45a514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 9 名、平愛梨。<br />\n這位綜藝傻大姊當年拿到了《20 世紀少年》電影版的女主角遠藤神乃，完全被動漫迷給嫌棄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e300a84f3e5.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e300a84f3e5.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1590b964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 8 名、水原希子。<br />\n作為模特兒，水原希子有著極具辨識度的臉蛋，但作為女演員的演技似乎就更褒貶不一了，尤其是她在《信長協奏曲》飾演信長的妹妹市，號稱戰國第一美女的扮相讓網友瘋狂吐槽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e2fc2d7c207.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e2fc2d7c207.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=216f9b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cs606825.vk.me/v606825320/228a/A0HkTgvU_oc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcs606825.vk.me%2Fv606825320%2F228a%2FA0HkTgvU_oc.jpg&h=f3146411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第 7 名、藤原纪香。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e30237cd63a.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e30237cd63a.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=5999e974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 6 名、本田翼。<br />\n模特兒轉戰女演員的另一代表，本田翼雖然也頻頻成為女主角，但只要說到演技不佳的女演員，她肯定榜上有名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e3030c750dd.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e3030c750dd.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=052b82f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 5 名、剛力彩芽。<br />\n從《古書堂事件手帖》到《大使閣下的料理人》，剛力彩芽一直都被漫畫迷封為毀戲不倦的強推女星，短髮的造型帶給了她極高的辨識度，但似乎卻讓她流失了觀眾緣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cs14114.vk.me/c7008/v7008405/1e531/aEqt9JCuVaI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcs14114.vk.me%2Fc7008%2Fv7008405%2F1e531%2FaEqt9JCuVaI.jpg&h=84908da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e3030e0d9a9.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e3030e0d9a9.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d79728e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 4 名、佐佐木希。<br />\n所有人都愛的清純女神佐佐木希，從模特兒轉戰日劇的她也是出了名的「演技下手」女星。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e3046a69ab5.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e3046a69ab5.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0a377e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 3 名、特林德爾&middot;玲奈。<br />\n日德混血兒特林德爾&middot;玲奈在前兩年因為極度可愛的臉蛋，而成為了超火紅的代言新星，這也讓她接到了不少戲劇邀約，但網友卻給她的演技相當低的評價。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e2fc2d04d3f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e2fc2d04d3f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=af8f7d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/CC2MkU.img?h=194&amp;w=300&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=t&amp;l=f&amp;f=jpg&amp;x=1461&amp;y=607\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FCC2MkU.img%3Fh%3D194%26w%3D300%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Dt%26l%3Df%26f%3Djpg%26x%3D1461%26y%3D607&h=2addbe04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第 2 名、篠田麻里子。<br />\n前 AKB48 人氣成員篠田麻里子在畢業之後，偶爾會在日劇中跑龍套一下，像是《ON 異常犯罪搜査官・藤堂比奈子》中火速領便當，但去年獲得好資源演出《火星異種》電影版，但觀眾似乎還是不太樂見她的演技。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e3050cc63fa.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e3050cc63fa.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=44b2a9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 1 名、前田敦子。<br />\n雖然之前在深夜劇《毒島百合子的赤裸裸日記》大尺度演出，並且獲得不錯的收視率，但這位前 AKB48 的王牌成員一直都是日本網友票選演技最差的女演員冠軍，或許也有參雜著一些「偶像出生就是原罪」的情節。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64381/58e3061865cef.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64381%2F58e3061865cef.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=6c74eed7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b0c5d4fa62a2be3d90808198c594ba0b38eb6a1","tid":188812,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"又係前田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4583a26f8b78f4b7197ee5ba5c1fc1559aa547","tid":188812,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得最難頂係本田翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <